  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dad\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd4 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Long fuel queues again",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the lack of fuel, long queues of vehicles could be seen near petrol stations across the country since the morning of today (26) and people were inconvenienced due to lack of fuel stock in many petrol stations.",
        "Many petrol stations were closed due to lack of fuel in Colombo and nearby petrol stations and Q.R. People had to queue for hours yesterday to get fuel for the system.",
        "People were inconvenient due to lack of diesel stocks even though there were stocks of petrol in some petrol stations.",
        "Some filling stations in Colombo Naraga received fuel this afternoon and many filling stations did not receive fuel, so the queues got longer."
      ],
